40:14.820 --> 40:19.332
People witness
these strange lights and UFOs

40:19.417 --> 40:22.877
above the Carnac stones
in France.

40:24.004 --> 40:27.498
Near Stonehenge in England,
each year,

40:27.583 --> 40:30.334
strange crop circles appear.

40:30.428 --> 40:33.671
