40:33.755 --> 40:37.434
you have mysterious lights,
UFO abductions,

40:37.518 --> 40:42.272
disappearances, time slips,
things like this taking place.

40:43.432 --> 40:46.767
Plasma UFOs, have been seen
and reported.

40:46.852 --> 40:49.571
And these continue to this day.

40:51.273 --> 40:56.536
CHILDRESS: Perhaps these
standing stones are storing energy,

40:56.620 --> 40:59.947
they're emitting energy
and with the right technology

41:00.040 --> 41:02.709
and instruments,
you can pick these stones up--

41:02.793 --> 41:05.628
These standing stones--
From hundreds of miles away.

41:06.964 --> 41:10.041
TSOUKALOS: The point is that
the standing stone formations

41:10.125 --> 41:12.710
that we find
all around the world

41:12.803 --> 41:18.382
are pieces of the puzzle
of the ancient astronaut theory,

41:18.476 --> 41:23.897
that long ago we received
visits from outer space

41:23.981 --> 41:26.390
and we were visited
by none other

41:26.475 --> 41:29.652
than our first teachers
on planet Earth.

41:30.905 --> 41:35.408
NARRATOR: Do the standing
stones found across the world represent

41:35.493 --> 41:39.070
the remains of a sophisticated
global electrical grid?

41:39.163 --> 41:41.581
One that exceeds
the most advanced technology

41:41.665 --> 41:42.999
we possess today?

41:44.168 --> 41:47.662
And if so, could Earth be part
of a universal network

41:47.755 --> 41:51.082
of space ports built
for interplanetary travel?

41:51.175 --> 41:55.253
Perhaps with further examination
of the ancient monoliths

41:55.337 --> 41:58.673
we will learn to harness
their power ourselves

41:58.757 --> 42:03.186
and continue the legacy
of our alien ancestors.

